{"description":"Aliru is very present within the Abstract ecosystem, he is an active Gigachad, often there to help the community.

He brings his touch of freshness and originality.

I appreciate him for his authenticity."}

{"description":"Met Envok back in the early days of the @abstractchain Discord. He was just spreading good vibes and calling out the farmers. Later on, we both earned the GIGA Chad role and connected on a personal level.

He taught me trading skills and has been super supportive in my content creation journey.

If you want a solid perspective on the crypto market no hype, no emotions, Envok’s your guy."}

