{
  "description": "Vitlus has been supporting and growing not only Ruyui but also Abstract since the very beginning: he’s an active member of the community, always aware of what’s going on, always ready to help, always moving the conversation forward.\nHe makes a real contribution, shares ideas, supports people, and helps projects grow. He respects the community and keeps his word.\nA true GigaChad and one of those people who make our ecosystem better every single day."
}

{
  "description": "I know Micka for a long time, we followed each other on X and always give best insights together

What I like most about Micka is that he is a true giga chad, his livestreams about abstract ecosystem are very deep and full of useful information for everyone

Appreciate the great work you do"
}

{
  "description": "Да, мы встретились в первые в Абстракт. Приятно наблюдать, как она поддерживает экосистему и людей внутри нее. Она играет в игры, стримит процесс и коллекционирует NFT + ко всему она не так давно присоединилась к Lil Pudgy, как холдер. Вот как выглядит настоящая искренняя поддержка"
